ELDER glanced at the silent WINDLORD and PERCEPTOR his optics dimming
for a moment. Finally he turned to LEGACY, "Send the pulse, that
should allow the Satellite's computer core to unlock."

"Acknowledged." LEGACY said as he walked over to one of the control
panels and began typing in a series of commands.

There was a small beep on the console in front of ELDER causing him to
look down. "I am picking up two Predacon signatures at the extreme
edge of our range." he said curiously.

ELDER pointed a a small set of mountains at the edge of their map. as
he looked up at WINDLORD and PERCEPTOR, "I need you two check it out."

(TAG)

- Preston
